import React from 'react'
import {NavFlex, LogoLink, NavLogo, BeRide} from './style'
import {GiFlamingTrident} from 'react-icons/gi'

const NavBar = () => {
    return (
        <NavFlex>
            <NavLogo>
                <LogoLink href="/">
                    <GiFlamingTrident/>  
                </LogoLink>
                <LogoLink href="/">
                    <BeRide>BeRide</BeRide>    
                </LogoLink>
            </NavLogo>

        </NavFlex>
    )
}

export default NavBar
